Namun, Nanmin sangat jauh.

227
00:14:49,080 --> 00:14:50,679
Aku ingin menemanimu.

228
00:14:51,400 --> 00:14:53,039
Anak dungu.

229
00:14:54,000 --> 00:14:56,679
Asalkan hidupmu baik,
hidup Nenek juga akan baik.

230
00:14:57,000 --> 00:14:59,080
Jangan mencemaskanku.

231
00:15:01,599 --> 00:15:03,080
Nenek hanya akan tanya padamu.

232
00:15:04,039 --> 00:15:05,520
Apakah kau bersedia?

233
00:15:06,159 --> 00:15:09,239
Jika kau bersedia, aku akan
memberimu dekret pernikahan.

234
00:15:20,479 --> 00:15:21,200
Ingat dioleskan.

235
00:15:44,080 --> 00:15:44,760
Baik.

236
00:15:45,559 --> 00:15:47,000
Aku ikuti keinginan Nenek.

237
00:15:49,960 --> 00:15:51,359
Baguslah.

238
00:15:52,640 --> 00:15:54,479
Kalau begitu, kami persiapkan dulu.

239
00:15:54,840 --> 00:15:57,520
Dua hari lagi, kami pergi
