putri pertama Bangsawan Dingbei?

368
00:25:14,000 --> 00:25:16,959
Jika lukisan hancur,
masih bisa dilukis ulang.

369
00:25:17,839 --> 00:25:20,760
Jika manusia hancur, maka takkan
ada kesempatan kedua lagi.

370
00:25:29,760 --> 00:25:30,560
Nona!

371
00:25:30,719 --> 00:25:31,439
Nona!

372
00:25:32,839 --> 00:25:33,359
Nona.

373
00:25:33,800 --> 00:25:35,160
Adipati Rahmat datang melamar.

374
00:25:35,839 --> 00:25:36,599
Apa?

375
00:25:45,920 --> 00:25:49,479
Adipati Rahmat sungguh mau
menikahi Su Su?

376
00:25:49,800 --> 00:25:50,800
Aku serius.

377
00:25:51,479 --> 00:25:52,439
Semoga Anda merestui.

378
00:25:52,640 --> 00:25:54,560
Kami hanya punya satu putri,
yaitu Su Su.

379
00:25:55,040 --> 00:25:57,719
Pernikahannya harus
disetujui olehnya.

380
00:25:58,199 --> 00:26:00,800
Kami masih harus tanya pada Su Su
tentang hal ini.

381
00:26:01,640 --> 00:26:03,239
Kalau begitu, aku pamit dulu.

382
00:26:03,700 --> 00:26:05,020
Kutunggu kabar baik dari kalian.

383
00:26:17,959 --> 00:26:18,719
Su Su!

384
00:26:25,120 --> 00:26:33,250
(Kediaman Bangsawan Dingbei)

385
00:26:38,400 --> 00:26:39,280
Kau pulang dulu.

386
00:26:46,560 --> 00:26:47,119
Tuan.

387
00:26:47,800 --> 00:26:49,760
Kenapa kau tiba-tiba
berubah pikiran?

388
00:26:54,479 --> 00:26:55,359
Hidup ini singkat.

389
00:26:56,900 --> 00:26:58,260
Kita sama-sama tak ingin menyesal.

390
00:27:00,620 --> 00:27:03,400
(Istana Ciyuan)

391
00:27:03,400 --> 00:27:04,600
Apakah benar Ibu Suri Agung...

392
00:27:04,600 --> 00:27:06,560
...suruh orang menggantung ini
beberapa hari lalu?

393
00:27:06,560 --> 00:27:07,040
Benar.

394
00:27:07,439 --> 00:27:10,640
Kasim Liu dari Istana Shoukang yang
langsung memerintahkan pelayan.

395
00:27:11,760 --> 00:27:15,280
Sepertinya Ibu Suri Agung sudah
menerimaku sebagai permaisuri.

396
00:27:24,920 --> 00:27:26,319
Apa perkataanmu benar?

397
00:27:27,000 --> 00:27:28,719
Meski mata-mata kita
di Istana Shoukang...

398
00:27:28,920 --> 00:27:31,520
...tak dengar langsung,
tapi Ibu Suri Agung...

399
00:27:31,520 --> 00:27:34,479
...sudah mengatur besok lusa membawa
Putri Agung ke Gunung Wanshou.

400
00:27:35,000 --> 00:27:37,520
Kini, Ibu Suri Agung masih bisa
mengurus apa lagi?

401
00:27:37,800 --> 00:27:39,319
Tentu saja pernikahan Putri Agung.

402
00:27:40,560 --> 00:27:43,760
Apa kau tahu siapa
yang Ibu Suri Agung pilih?

403
00:27:44,079 --> 00:27:46,439
Beberapa hari lalu,
Istana Shoukang adakan pesta.

404
00:27:46,760 --> 00:27:49,560
Hanya undang Adipati Rahmat
dan Putra Bangsawan Jinghai.

405
00:27:51,560 --> 00:27:52,439
Pantas saja.

406
00:27:53,040 --> 00:27:55,640
Pantas saja Kaisar menusuk
Putra Bangsawan Jinghai.

407
00:27:56,560 --> 00:27:58,000
Rupanya Ibu Suri Agung...

408
00:27:58,000 --> 00:28:00,620
