dengan Putra Bangsawan Jinghai.

409
00:28:00,620 --> 00:28:01,920
Sehingga Kaisar marah.

410
00:28:02,920 --> 00:28:03,479
Baihe.

411
00:28:04,040 --> 00:28:06,079
Besok pagi, kita pergi
ke Gunung Wanshou.

412
00:28:06,680 --> 00:28:09,920
Kita harus temui Ibu Suri lebih dulu
dari Jiang Baoning dan Ibu Suri Agung.

413
00:28:11,319 --> 00:28:13,479
Di hati Ibu Suri Agung,
hanya ada Jiang Baoning.

414
00:28:14,079 --> 00:28:15,400
Lepaskan semua lentera ini!

415
00:28:15,959 --> 00:28:17,160
Aku kesal melihatnya!

416
00:28:17,160 --> 00:28:18,820
(Istana Ciyuan)

417
00:28:18,870 --> 00:28:21,220
(Aula Qinzheng)

418
00:28:23,079 --> 00:28:24,560
